@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state "Idle" as Idle
Idle : entry/To action
Idle : do/Remain in same state
Idle : exit/Insert Card / Enter PIN

state "Card Inserted" as CardInserted
CardInserted : entry/Card Inserted
CardInserted : do/Prompt user to enter PIN
CardInserted : exit/PIN Entered / Invalid Card

state "Invalid Card" as InvalidCard
InvalidCard : entry/Invalid Card
InvalidCard : do/Return card and remain idle
InvalidCard : exit/Abnormal termination

state "PIN Entered" as PINEntered
PINEntered : entry/PIN Entered
PINEntered : do/Verify entered PIN against stored information
PINEntered : exit/PIN Verified / Invalid PIN

state "Invalid PIN" as InvalidPIN
InvalidPIN : entry/Invalid PIN
InvalidPIN : do/Return card and remain idle
InvalidPIN : exit/Abnormal termination

state "PIN Verified" as PINVerified
PINVerified : entry/PIN Verified
PINVerified : do/Provide options to the user
PINVerified : exit/Withdrawal / Other Options

state "Withdrawal" as Withdrawal
Withdrawal : entry/Withdrawal
Withdrawal : do/Process withdrawal request upon user approval
Withdrawal : exit/Dispense Cash / Cancel Transaction

state "Dispense Cash" as DispenseCash
DispenseCash : entry/Dispense Cash
DispenseCash : do/Dispense cash and print receipt for the transaction
DispenseCash : exit/Return Card / Complete Transaction

state "Complete Transaction" as CompleteTransaction
CompleteTransaction : entry/Complete Transaction
CompleteTransaction : do/Return user's card
CompleteTransaction : exit/Reset System / Idle

state "Cancel Transaction" as CancelTransaction
CancelTransaction : entry/Cancel Transaction
CancelTransaction : do/Return user's card and remain idle
CancelTransaction : exit/Abnormal termination

@enduml
